---

## Customization

### Colors
All colors are defined as CSS variables at the top of the `<style>` block:

```css
:root {
  --cream:    #f5f0e8;   /* page background */
  --ink:      #1a1714;   /* text, dark sections */
  --warm-mid: #7c6e5f;   /* secondary text */
  --gold:     #c8a96e;   /* accents, eyebrows */
  --rust:     #a84f2a;   /* CTA section, italic highlights */
  --pale:     #ede7db;   /* alternate section background */
}
```

### Links
Update these before launch:

- **Gallery links** — `href="#features"` placeholders throughout; replace with actual shop/gallery URLs
- **Amazon link** — points to `https://www.amazon.com`; replace with the direct *Thought Entropy* product URL
- **iExploreart link** — `https://iexploreart.com` in the footer

### Painting prices / titles
Each gallery card in the `#features` section contains a `.painting-card-price` span — update prices, dimensions, and availability status directly in the HTML.

---

## Deployment

This is a static file. It can be hosted anywhere:

- **Drag and drop:** Netlify Drop, Vercel, GitHub Pages
- **FTP/cPanel:** Upload `jfeelgood.html` as `index.html` to the web root
- **CDN:** Works as-is on any CDN that serves static HTML

No server-side processing required.

---

## Browser Support

Works in all modern browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge). The scroll-reveal animations use `IntersectionObserver`, which is supported in all evergreen browsers. No polyfills needed.

